{"tid":1847450,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］深圳灣管制站男廁疑現爆炸品　警封鎖現場嚴陣以待","createTime":"2020-01-28T05:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T07:58:20.000Z","uid":89966,"like":310,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"af2054487478e88b6f65e9b7697ceedc66fe718b","tid":1847450,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"深圳灣口岸管制站大樓，今午12時許，網傳相片多名警員圍封上址地下一個男廁，其後警方爆炸品處理課人員亦到場嚴陣以待。消息指，該個男廁內疑有爆炸品。<br />\n昨日(27日)20小時內接連發生兩宗廁所爆炸案，其中有人於通訊軟件Telegram上發文，承認在明愛醫院裝設相關可疑物品，並留言威脅要求本港醫護人員罷工。同時，網上亦流傳將會有行動針對「非鐵路連接嘅口岸」，東網記者正向警方了解事件，暫未知是否與過去兩案有關。<br />\n<br />\nFrom <a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=6ed98af0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200128/mobile/bkn-20200128124353454-0128_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200128%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200128124353454-0128_00822_001.html&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=067434b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200128/mobile/bkn-20200128124353454-0128_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7ccaaea1746682e90acddffe4950578a295b8a","tid":1847450,"uid":135689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555fe919175816ef39915df77cb892b4e0281c32","tid":1847450,"uid":171633,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:18:13.000Z","msg":"手足好耶！"},{"pid":"3b6ebd8b4c9714b6b509391c57be8af89b8aa589","tid":1847450,"uid":58174,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":3,