d":1847450,"uid":88578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"手足好波，核彈都不割。"},{"pid":"4372d1c2218229afefc4c4f7e39ee10a46e53ace","tid":1847450,"uid":237295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:27:48.000Z","msg":"多謝手足"},{"pid":"dc0dc24898aafd8f60f737680b48f9dbc9a1b5da","tid":1847450,"uid":108751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"手足好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1cbd78126dd2bd5ab93760cf6b5e1e7ded426e","tid":1847450,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"35a31b3cdde2a987989724ab71a54b52f14fb74e","tid":1847450,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:30:32.000Z","msg":"Source: 基本上已可斷言武漢肺炎係來自武漢P4實驗室<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/news.guo.offload.media/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/25133703/Brief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fnews.guo.offload.media%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F25133703%2FBrief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=be747e8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/news.guo.offload.media/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/25133703/Brief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n懶人包：<br />\n1. 武漢沙士病毒好可能係人工<br />\n<br />\n-佢同2017年浙江蝙蝠身上發現嘅冠狀病毒嘅E protein 100% 一樣 (相應嘅DNA 相似度都有225/228)，下一隻最接近嘅病毒已經只有低於95%一樣。<br />\n<br />\n病毒嘅基因複制同人類唔同；佢哋冇糾錯機制，發生變異機率相當大。即使E protein為保守序列，病毒品種相對不易產生變異，自然界中仍然非常唔可能有兩種冠狀病毒嘅E protein 完全一樣。SARS唔同亞種嘅E protein都有少量差別。<br />\n<br />\n-ORF8 基因通常病毒品種之間分別好大，2017浙江嗰隻嘅ORF8 同其他冠狀病毒最多只有60%似，但係同武漢沙士就有94.21%一樣<br />\n<br />\n2. 電腦推算武漢沙士病毒入侵人體嘅方式與SARS異常接近<br />\n<br />\nSARS入侵人體第一步，係病毒嘅S protein 痴落人體嘅ACE2 受體. 武漢沙士嘅S protein 整體上同SARS或者2017浙江嗰隻都唔似，但係真正痴落人體嗰部分就同沙士好似。最重要嗰五個氨基酸雖然同沙士有四個唔一樣，但係物理特性相似。電腦分析亦估算武漢沙士同人體ACE2 receptor 親和度非常高，只比SARS略低<br />\n<br />\n所以文章推斷為：有可能係有人參考沙士入侵呼吸道細胞ACE2 受體嘅方法，去改造2017年浙江蝙蝠身上發現嘅冠狀病毒，再放出自然環境（如武漢市場）繁殖一段短時間"},{"pid":"2aec744fc33a6e59b45b87ea0f03256b713cb286","tid":1847450,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc27104b826e530add2d4feadfa8b83f17955f5","tid":1847450,"uid":346478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"通左關"},{"pid":"6ab6f5763e935f2fc57cd4a759ed77950c5d33ed","tid":1847450,"uid":282625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"手足好波！"},{"pid":"fe787b2dddb144fcf9fe9d1f0e6499ba0f842d3d","tid":1847450,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壓力煲炸彈成本776元 「基地」製作教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d1a16aba26046092bc1a7ab462c8362914119e1","tid":1847450,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82a60d3982cfec7db6c69509c61117fc341b0d3b","tid":1847450,"uid":100494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8Qt95KUOX_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8Qt95KUOX_8&d=i